-seeking\ndelete algorithm is easily understandable and suitable for pedagogical\npurposes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Apr 2020 03:12:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Jun 2022 10:17:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 21 Jun 2022 02:40:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-22"}
