 and\nprejudice also appear to be related, though only weakly. Finally, anxiety\nappears in clusters related to social norms, suggesting that fears regarding\nimmigrants relates closely to expectations of others' behavior.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Apr 2020 05:01:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-10"}
